  <p class="install-note">
    See <a href={`https://github.com/${repo}/blob/main/docs/user-guide/installation.md`}>installation guide</a>
    for Docker and development setup.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .install-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
